    "id": 206,
    "name": "Visit Our Shop",
    "description": "<div><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-211975af-7fff-b5e9-77d3-fcd807938e7e\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:7pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Come and visit our friendly team and fully stocked stores at Pinxton. We are open:</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:7pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Monday- Friday: 8am - 5pm</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:7pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Saturday: 8:30am- 12:30pm.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:7pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">If you are after a specific agricultural part, our expert parts man, Steve, works Monday - Thursday. With his  knowledge, there will be no issue smoothly sourcing your desired part(s). Either bring them in, or email us an image to </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">office@buntingsagri.co.uk </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">and we will get in touch with you. </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br><br></span></p><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding-inline-start: 48px;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: circle; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;\" aria-level=\"2\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Rutland &amp; Hotline Electric Fencing and Energisers.</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: circle; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;\" aria-level=\"2\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Plastic &amp; Galvanised Wheelbarrows.</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: circle; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;\" aria-level=\"2\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Buckler safety and non safety dealer boots, lace up boots and wellingtons.</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: circle; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;\" aria-level=\"2\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Castle clothing range. From polo tops to winter coats, work trousers to overalls...</span></p></li><li dir=\"l