    "descriptionText": "Come and visit our friendly team and fully stocked stores at Pinxton. We are open: Monday- Friday: 8am - 5pm Saturday: 8:30am- 12:30pm. If you are after a specific agricultural part, our expert parts man, Steve, works Monday - Thursday. With his knowledge, there will be no issue smoothly sourcing your desired part(s). Either bring them in, or email us an image to office@buntingsagri.co.uk and we will get in touch with you. Rutland &amp; Hotline Electric Fencing and Energisers. Plastic &amp; Galvanised Wheelbarrows. Buckler safety and non safety dealer boots, lace up boots and wellingtons. Castle clothing range. From polo tops to winter coats, work trousers to overalls... 20kg Amenity, Paddock or Agricultural Grass Seed Bags. Gate furniture and hardware. Water Pipe &amp; Fittings Protek bird scaring products Lodi Rat Bait, ranging from 150g grain and paste formulations to ..kg boxes. For large quantities please bring along your CRRU approved certificate or red tractor number. Tractor Batteries and battery chargers Machine filters &amp; belts Millers Oil in 5L or 20L Drums PTO- complete shafts, guards &amp; parts Vehicle &amp; Building Lighting Forks, brushes, shovels, sledgehammers, post knockers, knapsacks... Efco chainsaws and chains Seat covers for tractors, trucks and diggers. Paint and creosote. And much more! If in doubt, feel free to drop us a message on messenger or give us a call.",
